      <description>Lets look at how we might take input from either a file or the keyboard. Our goal is that the program uses the first command line argument for input if it is a file. If no argument is given it should use the keyboard. If the first command line argument is not a file, or if an error occurs, the program should print &amp;ldquo;Error processing the first argument as a file&amp;rdquo;.</description>
